    public class RemoteSyncManager
extends AbstractSyncManager
    Implementation of a sync service that passes its functionality off to a remote sync manager over a TCP connection

        public void addRPCListener(IRPCListener listener)
        从接口复制的说明: ISyncService
        Listener to RPC connections, used in simple Fault tolerance module, or other modules that need cluster monitor nodes (connect and disconnect). The listener is dispatched at connected or disconnected events. The listener inform the node id of connected or disconnected nodes on cluster.
